reviewText:
Well, I enjoyed the anime. Cute looking characters but the ending... It bothers me. There is no closure.
But i enjoyed the ride it took me on.
English subtitles, but it is the full series
Awesome!  I can only hope they finish the series so i can complete my collection

The Lost Canvas is a magnificent series, and holds up a lot better than the original series. Unlike the japanese releases there are no extras however, which is a shame. Hence the grade, as this review is about the product, not the series itself.
Great series!  Exceeded my expectations.  However, the Saint Seiya creators need to kick the habit of leaving us hanging!  Provide a complete series!
Great series, still waiting for it to be completed.
Finally being able to own this series is awesome. This version has no dub but comes with English subtitles. If your a fan of Saint seiya you will enjoy the lost canvas.
It is in Japanese. So be careful if your thinking about buying one.
